PROGRAM FinalGeneralizedAudit
    ARENA main_arena 4096
    WAVELET W1 IN main_arena
    WAVELET W2 IN main_arena
    CONNECT W1 W2

    ! 1. Use high-level GENERATE with generalized parameters
    ! Parameters are tuned for resonance: Domain=4919, Link=43690, Cost=48059
    GENERATE W1 W2 4919 43690 48059

    IONIZE W1 W2
    MAGNETIZE W1 W2
    
    ! 2. Activation
    SEAL_HEADER W1
    SEAL_HEADER W2
    ACTIVATE_YANG W1 12345
    ACTIVATE_YANG W2 12345

    ! 3. Generalized Pulse
    PULSE W1 ICHI
    PULSE W2 ICHI

    ! 4. Generalized Reduction
    DOMAIN_REDUCE main_arena 12 0 2026

    LOG_TELEMETRY "Final Generalized Audit Complete"
END PROGRAM
